{"tid":944532,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"恆指30,000點不是夢","createTime":"2018-12-17T08:17:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-18T07:01:35.000Z","uid":207621,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5476461b1e1f00df97a628013b30f7fd667a2d70","tid":944532,"uid":207621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T08:17:44.000Z","msg":"恆指明年底目標30,000點<br />\n<br />\n匯豐私人銀行亞洲區首席市場策略師范卓雲在記者會上表示，由於中美正進行貿易判談，預期環球股市在明年首季仍會較為波動，但預料美國加息周期將在明年完結，美元匯率見頂，將對新興及亞洲市場股債有支持，對中國、新加坡及印度股票評級為超配。<br />\n<br />\n她提到，受中美貿易磨擦影響，預期明年中國出口增長將會放緩至3.5%，人民幣匯率則會靠穩及溫和下降，不會出現大幅下跌，料至明年底人民幣兌美元將貶值至7.1的水平。"},{"pid":"7c9b0356a83c6a1896fc9d5646b787059c31b7da","tid":944532,"uid":174207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T08:35:46.000Z","msg":"美期跌都無影響  牛得"},{"pid":"0a2c867c686f2884e33fd0c6b4578419b3ecee26","tid":944532,"uid":110988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T08:42:34.000Z","msg":"上哂電視接受訪問 唔升會唔會太柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61df6102651af743dd490819998c968d507c9593","tid":944532,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T08:57:38.000Z","msg":"匯豐證券對恒指2018年底目標3萬點 第四季籲吸平保、中海油等 <br />\n17年10月3日 <br />\n<br />\n匯豐證券對恒指2018年底目標30000點，國企指數目標則為12500點。另外對上證綜指目標設於3800點，MSCI中國目標設94，認為催化劑主要來自改革推動，風險是宏觀經濟及企業盈利增長慢過預期。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.quamnet.com/newscontent.action?articleId=5414368\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.quamnet.com%2Fnewscontent.action%3FarticleId%3D5414368&d=bVhSs0u1UTjocNzuugnzMDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=b007f76e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.quamnet.com/newscontent.action?articleId=5414368</a><br />\n<br />\n又推遲多一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f206ed46017bdf0f1d946bfe838ae4e42bc156fc","tid":944532,"uid":32586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61df610